{{version031}}
{{flavour|Creates several living, autonomous spells, which cast themselves at the first foe to enter their range. Once cast, they dissipate.}}

'''Conjure Living Spells''' summons living spell monsters. Each type of [[walking tome]] uses a different spell. They behave like [[Foxfire]]s: each living spell has 1-2 HP, but on contact with an enemy, they'll cast their respective spell. Note that the living spells themselves are unaffected by [[silence]]. Crystal tomes summon 1-2 living spells; the other tomes summon 2-3 living spells.

{{monsters with spell}}

==History==
*Prior to [[0.31]], walking tomes could sustain up to 6 living spells at once. Also, crystal tomes will only cast 1-2 spells.
*Conjure Living Spells was introduced in [[0.28]], along with walking tomes.

[[Category: Monster spells]]
